This directory contains code derived from Palhelm's backend/internal/sav
package at commit e099e8afe4823d6cf6b371e5e3938955e5a1becd:

    https://github.com/8tp/palhelm/tree/e099e8afe4823d6cf6b371e5e3938955e5a1becd/backend/internal/sav

Copyright 2026 Palhelm contributors. Palhelm is licensed under the Apache
License, Version 2.0. A copy is included as LICENSE in this directory.

The port was modified to expose a roster-only Reader API, require an explicit
caller-supplied Oodle library, avoid all network and write operations, read
persisted player transforms/date-times, enforce bounded input/output, and
support the Palworld July 2026 guild-role layout.

No Palworld save, account identifier, player name, proprietary Oodle binary,
or GPL parser code is included in this directory.
